co.paralleluniverse.xst

Class ExtendedStackTrace

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.paralleluniverse.xst.ExtendedStackTrace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<ExtendedStackTraceElement>

    public class ExtendedStackTrace
extends Object
implements Iterable<ExtendedStackTraceElement>
    Represents a captured stack trace which contains more information than that returned by Throwable.getStackTrace(). The extended information is captured on a best-effort basis, and depends on the JVM used.
